## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **teprotumumab Tepezza 2020** = first FDA IGF-1R mAb TED — Horizon/Amgen. OPTIC + OPTIC-X trials proptosis + diplopia + CAS 호전. paradigm shift from corticosteroid 1L 이래. quantum-VQE 의 IGF-1R pocket 직접 fit.
2. **IGF-1R + TSHR cross-talk** = TED 의 핵심 paradigm — orbital fibroblast 에서 IGF-1R + TSHR heterodimer 형성 + autoantibody-mediated activation. quantum-VQE 의 heterodimer interface modeling 한정.
3. **linsitinib (OSI Pharm — re-purposed)** = IGF-1R small molecule oral, originally cancer 개발 → TED 재활용 Phase 2/3. teprotumumab IV 의 oral alternative.
4. **VRDN-001/VRDN-003 (Viridian) Phase 3 + 2024** = IGF-1R mAb next-gen short course + SC 제형. teprotumumab 대비 dosing schedule + administration improvement.
5. **batoclimab IMVT-1402 FcRn TED Phase 3** = FcRn paradigm — IgG autoantibody 감소 통한 TED + myasthenia + ITP cross-disease 적응증. quantum-VQE 의 FcRn pocket cross-leverage.
6. **tocilizumab IL-6R off-label TED** = small RCT + retrospective evidence — refractory TED 에서 일부 효과. cross-systemic_sclerosis_specific + inflammatory_arthritis IL-6R pathway 공유.
7. **rituximab anti-CD20 off-label TED** = refractory + steroid-resistant TED — 작은 RCT 결과 mixed. cross-bone_marrow_failure CD20 mechanism 공유.
8. **methylprednisolone IV pulse 500mg+ EUGOGO** = active TED 1L standard. EU EUGOGO guideline + 한국 framework 동일. 그러나 부작용 + relapse 부담.
9. **selenium mild TED EUGOGO 1차예방** = mild active TED 에서 selenium 200mcg/day 6mo — quality of life + progression 감소. low-cost adjunct.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, TED 임상 의미 한정. teprotumumab 의 hearing loss + hyperglycemia 부작용 회피 가 hxq-ted-igf1r-002 의 design rationale.

